<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天啊！”汤姆想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>护城河里有很多鳄鱼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有些鳄鱼睡着了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27247</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他的在水里游来游去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27248</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31210</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德克用力拍了一下汤姆的肩膀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31211</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呦！”汤姆大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他差点儿掉到河里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德克抓住了汤姆的袍子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41772</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的笨咒语一点儿也没用。”德克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你最好快点儿想个别的主意！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆咽了口口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没问题！”他说，“我再想个咒语！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛丽公主又哭了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的皇冠！永远都找不回来了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83539</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆握紧了双手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83540</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88960</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么办呢？”他想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，他只能又举起了魔杖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“掉下去的皇冠！”他高叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“落在我手里！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆伸出了一只手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他满怀希望地盯着黑暗的河水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！”他大叫了一声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>皇冠从河水里升了起来，每个人都开始鼓掌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！汤姆做到了！”一个仆人低声地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126980</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130762</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哼！”德克不高兴地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130763</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛丽公主擦去了眼泪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134060</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请再等一会儿，各位！”汤姆大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142107</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把手放在河水上方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142108</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会拿到皇冠！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149642</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，汤姆看到了另一个东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149643</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你这个傻瓜！”德克大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”汤姆小声地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170031</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“皇冠出现了……在很饿的鳄鱼头上！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>